{"tid":847593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【封殺港獨】連儂牆風波 學生會圍大學高層求對話爆混亂","createTime":"2018-10-04T09:33:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T08:07:11.000Z","uid":40628,"like":56,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"2d9b124f79f137ab26bfdf1376f767fe804e0a63","tid":847593,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T09:33:50.000Z","msg":"【封殺港獨】連儂牆風波 學生會圍大學高層求對話爆混亂<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n理大「連儂牆」風波愈演愈烈，理大學生會9月底將校內半幅民主牆劃為「連儂牆」，讓同學以便條留言方式記念4年前的雨傘運動。後來疑因有同學在牆上張貼港獨言論，觸及校方神經，校方屢次在「連儂牆」釘上紅色畫紙遮蓋，亦有不明人士撕毀港獨字眼。理大學務長莫志明其後表示，民主牆同屬大學管轄範圍，因「連儂牆」不合當初賦予學生會管理的安排，故移除相關言論，被學生會炮轟打壓校內言論自由。理大學生會今午到校長辦公室門外，要求校長唐偉章公開與學生會對話。校方人員與學生發生推撞，混亂中多人倒地。<br />\n<br />\n今午2時，理大學生會會長林穎恒先手持喇叭，在副校長樓層辦公室高喊要求大學高層對話。其後林與理大學生校董李傲然衝入校長辦公室樓層，拍門要求管理層交代「連儂牆」被校方釘上紅色畫紙一事。港大學生會會長黃程鋒亦有到場聲援。<br />\n<br />\n其後理大副校長（學生事務）沈岐文及莫志明到場調解。林要求2人馬上開會談判，並勸喻同學離去；李要求兩人承諾民主牆管理權屬學生會而非校方，惟沈堅稱需待本周六下午4點開會討論，拒絕即時回應事件。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在場宣稱並不隷屬任何組織的關同學其後激動地說：「拆咗我哋民主牆，仲同我哋講冷靜？」他又謂「書都可以唔讀、監都可以坐、警察嚟我都唔驚，但係我今日一定要上到去」。<br />\n<br />\n雙方爭持多時，數名保安其後奉命到場戒備。沈及莫以開會為由，試圖離開校長辦公室樓層，期間與學生等人發生推撞。沈及林二人雙雙倒地，林其後向沈道歉，但堅持不讓二人離開。推撞期間亦有保安員倒地，左腳受傷。校方其後開放一間會議室，並答允與學生代表舉行閉門會議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/04/173234_9c35c31e203f7bf6c00c91681ed6080d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F04%2F173234_9c35c31e203f7bf6c00c91681ed6080d.jpg&h=4472f4c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/04/173237_42e20c6429448f25132b5dcc4b8aab09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F04%2F173237_42e20c6429448f25132b5dcc4b8aab09.jpg&h=817ad4a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/04/173239_72d7c25cdb8586dc0149f88a13588957.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F04%2F173239_72d7c25cdb8586dc0149f88a13588957.jpg&h=8ca3e629&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/04/173241_f7b2a773f683c955494e3c0f4ce0b670.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F04%2F173241_f7b2a773f683c955494e3c0f4ce0b670.jpg&h=2c9ccd65&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/04/173249_7921c4aad4662e066f9a9423e7bd8943.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F04%2F173249_7921c4aad4662e066f9a9423e7bd8943.jpg&h=9910e3a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181004/58755415\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181004%2F58755415&d=8BteI%2Bf9ky9hy%2B9tl%2BrAfWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=20d9cd0a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181004%2F58755415&h=526126e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181004/58755415</a>"},{"pid":"6d229e1e2ede435fb3a9e025cf312a833addb135","tid":847593,"uid":28366,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T09:34:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3cfa5d42c55df78f1966cf7e5bd61740279dd27","tid":847593,"uid":88737,"like":10,"dislike":4,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T09:44:30.000Z","msg":"關蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21a74128789e0135b11cac41eb1b480f72459682","tid":847593,"uid":2436,"like":5,"dislike":47,"score":-42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T09:45:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d325e